description: The little cart grew up to be a truck, but is still cooking up the sameclassic sandwiches with a gourmet twist. Their Delmonico Sandwich features grilled and sliced Delmonico steak, fresh Italian chimichurri, and jalapeno slaw on a grilled french roll. For veggie lovers, they also offer a plate of select marinated garden veggies! Don't skip out on their homemade pita chips which make a great addition to any meal!
name: The Burgh Bites Cart
